Hi Carol, glad to meet you!



Robin





----- Original Message ----- 

From: Carol B. &lt;mailto:cbreck@...&gt;  

To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com 

Sent: Saturday, January 19, 2008 11:43 AM

Subject: [EVP-ITC] Introducing myself



Hello all,

My name is Carol and I&#39;ve been an investigator for 10+ years. I&#39;m new to
the Frank&#39;s box device, and am totally fascinated by it! My husband works
in recording studios and is willing to build me my first box. I would
like to work with the RS hack too. I&#39;ve got many great class a evp&#39;s from
my dvr...but I&#39;m really looking forwards to working with Frank&#39;s Box. 
Glad to meet y&#39;all.

Carol B.




